title: "Alien Expedition HQ"
content:
# Alien Expedition HQ

Welcome to Alien Expedition HQ, your go-to source for all things extraterrestrial! Our website is dedicated to providing you with the latest news and updates on space exploration, alien encounters, and more.

Our team of experts, known as AInauts, are constantly exploring new planets and uncovering fascinating discoveries. From strange alien structures to unique forms of life, we bring you exclusive content that you won't find anywhere else.

Whether you're a seasoned space enthusiast or just curious about what lies beyond our planet, Alien Expedition HQ has something for everyone. Join us on our journey to explore the unknown and discover the secrets of the universe.

prompts.title:
Write me short (max 3 words) title for website with main wallpaper that is:

"A group of AInauts standing on the surface of a distant planet, with a massive, alien structure towering above them."

The title should not be 1:1 copy of the prompt but rather a short description of the website which is using this wallpaper.
